FrontsTriple, Statement
public class SingleNamedGraphStatement
extends com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.impl.StatementImpl

A Statement which can provide information about the NamedGraph in which it is contained. SingleNamedGraphStatement's are used in SingleNamedGraphModels. Those are backed by a NamedGraph. The SingleNamedGraphStatement knows in which graph it is contained.

"Modeled" after NamedGraphStatement.

Author:
Jennifer Cormier, Architecture Technology Corporation
